SMS,Broadcast,is,an,Australian,SMS,provider,One,noteworthy,feature,of,the,service,is,that,users,are,not,charged,for,any,undeliverable,SMS,messages,Users,can,integrate,SMS,Broadcast,s,capabilities,into,their,own,applications,using,the,SMS,Broadcast,API,for,no,additional,charge,Possible,uses,for,the,API,include,providing,notifications,to,customers,verifying,customers,phone,numbers,sending,SMS,to,end,users,when,they,log,in,and,simply,sending,and,receiving,messages